---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: A practical, systems-focused publication on how AI actually gets deployed inside real organizations — workflow optimization, operational reliability, and automation architecture.
---
<header class="section section-dark blog-index-header">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <a class="back-link" href="/">&larr; Rod Neufeld</a>
    <p class="eyebrow">Rod Neufeld</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title accent">AI in Operations</h1>
    <p class="blog-tagline">Not the voice of reason. Just not an unreasonable one.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="section section-light">
  <div class="container narrow">
    {% if collections.posts.length %}
      <div class="post-list">
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <article class="post-card">
          <a class="post-card-link" href="{{ post.url }}">
            <p class="post-card-date">
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</time>
            </p>
            <h2 class="post-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            {% if post.data.description %}
            <p class="post-card-description">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            <span class="post-card-cta">Read &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <p class="no-posts">First post coming Monday.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</main>
